sub_title: Head of Paid Search at TRGT Digital
summary:
Previous Experience: Performance Director at TRGT Digital, International Account Manage at Total Media, Digital Marketing Manager at Getty Images, Digital Specialist at Secret Escapes, Digital Executive at Flashbay, Consultancy projects for Visma Corporation and Bj√∏rg Jewellery.

Education: MA E-Marketing and Social Media, BA International Business, BA International Marketing.

Personality: Positive and driven to achieve my goals. I am a fast learner, creative, optimistic, highly motivated and passionate about marketing. 

Skills: PPC, SEA, Display Marketing, Content Marketing, Paid Social Media, Email Marketing, Media Planning & Strategy, SEO, Data & Market Analysis, International Business and Marketing.

Languages: Native Norwegian, fluent written and spoken English, professional proficiency in Danish and Swedish, and currently also learning Dutch.
